  <summary date="2021-05-28T15:45:39Z" status="Introduced in House">Safeguarding Oil and Gas Leasing and Permitting Act of 2021

This bill requires the President and the Department of the Interior to obtain the approval of Congress before implementing a moratorium on oil and gas leasing in the Gulf of Mexico region of the outer Continental Shelf.</summary>
